  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SteamDolls is a steampunk inspired metroidvania game with a grimy touch of brutality, featuring a star-studded voice cast, including David Hayter, Christopher Randolph, and Jennifer Hale. This is a free prologue demo which... <i>OH RIGHT, GET IT! WE ALL ALL KNOW THE STORY!</i> <strong>This is now THE WHISPER speaking:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"A concept demo...now what's that? Something interesting, I suppose. Ha! What started as an old, MUCH OUTDATED TEASER is now a <strong>COMPLETE DEMO. </strong>Yes, yes indeed...the game has taken many turns, so how could we just leave our dear fans without something to <strong>ENTERTAIN THEMSELVES</strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This little concept demo is now a full fledged introductory demo...it features a PROLOGUE. Something reminiscent of what to expect from STEAMDOLLS in the NEAR FUTURE. We encourage you to...join along...Maybe you'll like what you see. There's always more, you know\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/b93091c57c26e0adfeb57a0c027a7db9.avif?t=1728645881\" width=600 height=107 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Novel stealth-lite gameplay mixed with platforming and brutal action</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/9d7061b2200424d6c1c430ced7241bda.poster.avif?t=1728645881\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/9d7061b2200424d6c1c430ced7241bda.webm?t=1728645881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/9d7061b2200424d6c1c430ced7241bda.mp4?t=1728645881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gruesome finishers and combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/87bf658acb53372e53dc8430eea2481b.poster.avif?t=1728645881\" width=640 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/87bf658acb53372e53dc8430eea2481b.webm?t=1728645881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/87bf658acb53372e53dc8430eea2481b.mp4?t=1728645881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your hacking skills to experience the memories of the world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/7e84ab37211465ed11fee88b0f202876.poster.avif?t=1728645881\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/7e84ab37211465ed11fee88b0f202876.webm?t=1728645881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/7e84ab37211465ed11fee88b0f202876.mp4?t=1728645881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful comic book-inspired 2D meets 3D aesthetics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vast world to explore, filled with secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AAA voice cast, including David Hayter (Solid Snake) as the voice of The Whisper.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn Cutscenes for the narrative parts mixed with 3D cinematic inserts</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SteamDolls is a steampunk inspired metroidvania game with a grimy touch of brutality, featuring a star-studded voice cast, including David Hayter, Christopher Randolph, and Jennifer Hale. This is a free prologue demo which... <i>OH RIGHT, GET IT! WE ALL ALL KNOW THE STORY!</i> <strong>This is now THE WHISPER speaking:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"A concept demo...now what's that? Something interesting, I suppose. Ha! What started as an old, MUCH OUTDATED TEASER is now a <strong>COMPLETE DEMO. </strong>Yes, yes indeed...the game has taken many turns, so how could we just leave our dear fans without something to <strong>ENTERTAIN THEMSELVES</strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This little concept demo is now a full fledged introductory demo...it features a PROLOGUE. Something reminiscent of what to expect from STEAMDOLLS in the NEAR FUTURE. We encourage you to...join along...Maybe you'll like what you see. There's always more, you know\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/b93091c57c26e0adfeb57a0c027a7db9.avif?t=1728645881\" width=600 height=107 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Novel stealth-lite gameplay mixed with platforming and brutal action</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/9d7061b2200424d6c1c430ced7241bda.poster.avif?t=1728645881\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030760/extras/9d7061b2200424d6c1c430ced7241bda.webm?t=1728645881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/10